_sText:
This is my first map. It is kind of short, but it is extremely hard. Since this is my first map, I did not expect it to go as well as it did. Even though the map might not look too good, I think it turned out okay.

The map has:
1 Smoke-trail
1-Flash-trail
1 Deagle-trail

The end of the map contains: Kill all(Troll), Frags (99) and a hard bonus (99+ frags)

To finish the map, the thing you mostly need is bhopping, so if you're good at that, you propably can finish my map. :)

I didn't add any music too the map itself, since I personally hate when the music is disturbing my own music from Spotify.
